"loader.add_css('price', 'p#price', re='the price is (.*)')"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/loader/__init__.py:docstring of
#: itemloaders.ItemLoader.add_jmes:1
msgid ""
"Similar to :meth:`ItemLoader.add_value` but receives a JMESPath selector "
"instead of a value, which is used to extract a list of unicode strings from "
"the selector associated with this :class:`ItemLoader`."
